headline: Are Wall Street Analysts Predicting Public Service Enterprise Stock Will Climb or Sink?
summary: Despite Public Service Enterprise's underperformance relative to the broader market over the past year, Wall Street analysts maintain a moderately optimistic outlook about the stock’s prospects.
